1.0.0 (2014-05-21) - Initial Release
+ linux: Debian up-to-date minimal environment
+ nginx: initial configuration (@github: arut/nginx-rtmp-module)
+ nginx-rtmp-module: basic hls support
+ nginx-rtmp-module: basic dash support
+ ffmpeg: live channel transcoding
+ ffmpeg: live channel screenshot capture
+ ffmpeg: live channel record transcoding
+ web interface: Bootstrap based interface
+ web interface: live channels listing
+ web interface: recorded videos listing
+ web interface: multiplatform player for live channels and recorded videos
+ web interface: live channels json api
